Package: CompMod
Title: Comparable Company Analysis Tools for Valuation
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jeb", "Dee", , "deej@lawrence.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for performing comparable company (comps) analysis,
    a core valuation methodology in investment banking and equity research.
    Functions support reading standardized valuation data from Excel, computing
    key trading multiples, and summarizing peer group statistics to support
    implied valuation ranges.
